What is certain is that an application of hemlock to the breasts of women in childbed dries up their milk, and to rub it on the testacles at the time of puberty acts as an antaphrodisiac. I should not like to give directions about remedies in which hemlock is recommended to be taken by the mouth. The most powerful hemlock grows at Susa in Parthia3 the next in Laconia, Crete and Asia3 in Greece however the strongest is found around Megara, after which comes that of Attica.
